pathway.author: [Chris, DeSl, Egonw, Khanspers, AlexanderPico, Finterly, Eweitz]

comments.content: Formation of a blood clot by arachidonic acid. This pathway also shows various stimulants/inhibitors that have an effect on the pathway, while also showing the two compounds which respectively cause vasoconstriction/vasodilation and inhibit/stimulate platelet aggregation.

pathway.name: Blood clotting and drug effects
